ZH: 我们这个夏天准备到山区去避暑。
EN: We are planning to go to the mountains to escape the summer heat this year.

ZH: 暑假期间，许多人会选择去海边的度假村避暑。
EN: During the summer vacation, many people choose to go to seaside resorts to escape the heat.

ZH: 过去，避暑的人们通常选择高山或沿海地区。
EN: In the past, people who wanted to escape the summer heat usually chose mountainous or coastal areas.

ZH: 大家都喜欢在湖边避暑，享受湖水带来的凉爽感觉。
EN: Everyone loves to escape the summer heat by the lake and enjoy the coolness it brings.

ZH: 去年夏天，我和我的家人一起去了一个宁静的山区小镇避暑。
EN: Last summer, my family and I went to a peaceful mountain town to escape the heat.

ZH: 没有什么比在山上呼吸到新鲜空气更能避暑的了。
EN: There is nothing better than breathing in fresh air on the mountains to escape the summer heat.

ZH: 大多数人都会选择在夏季去避暑胜地度假。
EN: Most people choose to go to summer resorts to escape the heat.

ZH: 避暑胜地通常会提供各种户外活动选择，满足游客的需求。
EN: Summer resorts usually offer various outdoor activities to meet the needs of tourists.

ZH: 清晨的时候，人们可以在海滩上散步避暑。
EN: In the early morning, people can take a walk on the beach to escape the summer heat.

ZH: 在夏季，许多城市的居民会到郊外农庄避暑。
EN: In the summer, many city residents escape to rural farms to escape the heat.

ZH: 我学校的学生会在夏天举办一个避暑野营活动。
EN: The student council at my school is organizing a summer camping trip to escape the heat.

ZH: 有人建议在避暑胜地度假时多喝水，以保持身体水分。
EN: It is advised to drink plenty of water while on vacation in summer resorts to stay hydrated.

ZH: 去避暑胜地度假需要提前预订酒店，以免没有空房间。
EN: It is necessary to book hotels in advance when going on a vacation to summer resorts to avoid no availability.

ZH: 避暑胜地的游客可以尽情享受悬崖索道的刺激体验。
EN: Tourists at summer resorts can enjoy the thrilling experience of cliff cable cars.

ZH: 在夏季度假，我更喜欢选择避暑的山区而不是湖边。
EN: When going on a summer vacation, I prefer choosing mountainous areas to escape the heat rather than the lakeside.

ZH: 这个国家的南部地区是一个受人们喜爱的度假避暑胜地。
EN: The southern region of this country is a popular vacation and summer escape spot.

ZH: 我们邀请几个好友一起去避暑胜地，度过愉快的假期。
EN: We invited a few friends to go to a summer resort together and have a pleasant vacation.

ZH: 在高温的夏季，人们会选择在凉爽的森林里避暑。
EN: In the hot summer, people choose to escape the heat by staying in the cool forests.

ZH: 避暑旅行是一个很好的放松身心的方式。
EN: Taking a summer escape trip is a great way to relax both physically and mentally.

ZH: 城市里的人们经常会到公园里避暑，享受大自然的宁静。
EN: People living in the cities often escape to parks to enjoy the tranquility of nature and escape the summer heat.
